               This program is Shareware. Please copy it...

    If you find it useful, please send DM15 or $10 to the upper adress.
Then you will become a registered user of this product. If you add a blank
         disc, I will send it back to you with Version 1.0 of the 
  Paccer Level - Editor, including a 100% Save option for your self made
